    "DESCRIPTION" : {

    },
    "Dhikr (ذِكر) is a powerful spiritual act that nurtures the soul, polishes the heart, and brings one into divine presence. It is a means of drawing near to Allah ﷻ, increasing one’s reward, and protecting oneself from the whispers of Shaytaan. Dhikr revives the heart and is beloved to the Most Merciful." : {

    },
    "Dhikr is the heartbeat of the believer. It brings light to the face, peace to the soul, and strength to endure trials. It is a shield in times of hardship and a ladder to the nearness of Allah ﷻ." : {

    },
